{"TopicId":209415,"ForumId":32,"TopicTitle":"What do you Like Most About KSP?","CreatedByName":"Kerbalsaurus","CreatedById":222386,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-08-18T14:41:20Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Kerbalsaurus","CreatedById":222386,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-08-18T14:41:20Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIn my opinion, it has to be the Kerbals themselves. It\u2019s fun to build a rocket, watch you Kerbals almost crap themselves at launch, and then see them smiling the rest of the way.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"swjr-swis","CreatedById":152460,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-08-18T15:13:41Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe design/build/test/improve/repeat cycle.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI do realize part of that isn\u0027t even inherent to KSP, I inflict it on myself... but the game facilitates it, and it\u0027s something I enjoy (obsess over?) a lot.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAs for the kerbals: I think they are squandering a big opportunity if they never come out with Kerbal RTS, Kerbal Interplanetary Survival, Kerbal Olympics, and sure, why not, Kerbal Train Simulator.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Curveball Anders","CreatedById":107529,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-08-18T15:16:48Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224165173\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022209415\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221660835621\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022152460\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022swjr-swis\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nJust now, swjr-swis said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe design/build/test/improve/repeat cycle.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPersonally I\u0027d say dream/plan/design/test/improve/repeat.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Caerfinon","CreatedById":207619,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-08-18T15:22:04Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022FGbLcOg.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002268.03\u0022 height=\u0022500\u0022 width=\u0022735\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/FGbLcOg.png\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI think I\u0027ve made my point....\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Kerbalsaurus","CreatedById":222386,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-08-18T15:39:36Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224165173\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022209415\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221660835621\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022152460\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022swjr-swis\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n19 minutes ago, swjr-swis said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe design/build/test/improve/repeat cycle.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI like that too, minus the testing part. My Kerbal \u003Cs\u003Evictims\u003C/s\u003E participants never go on correctly tested rockets. It worked for the Soviet Union, so why can\u0027t it work for me?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"swjr-swis","CreatedById":152460,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-08-18T16:09:05Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224165193\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022209415\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221660837176\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022222386\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Kerbalsaurus\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n24 minutes ago, Kerbalsaurus said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt worked for the Soviet Union, so why can\u0027t it work for me?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIn Soviet Russia, rocket tests YOU.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:10px;\u0022\u003E(sorry, been ages since I got a good excuse to use that...)\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}